# Cloudflare Pages response headers. Baseline security headers for all responses.
# NOTE: a full Content-Security-Policy is intentionally deferred — it must be crafted
# and tested against the Google Identity Services + Gmail/Drive API calls (and the
# service worker) so it doesn't break sign-in. Track that as a follow-up.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
